                "text": "It seems there was an issue accessing the news stories directly. However, here's how you can manually find the latest news story from Microsoft's news website:\n\n1. Go to [https://news.microsoft.com](https://news.microsoft.com)\n2. At the top of the page, locate and click on the \"What's new today\" link.\n3. This will show you the most recent news stories.\n4. The first news story listed is typically the latest; click on it to view details.\n\nIf you'd like, I can try again or guide you step-by-step to view and summarize the latest story. Would you like me to attempt the automation again, or do you prefer a manual walkthrough?",
